"{\"uid\": \"straitstimes.com-sport-not-a-love-affair-olympic-games-kick-off-to-cool-reception-from-parisians\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Choose edition  Search  singapore  asia  world  opinion  life  business  sport  Visual  Podcasts  SPH Rewards  STClassifieds  Paid press releases  Advertise with us  FAQs  Contact us  Sign up now:Get the biggest sports news in your inbox  The Paris Olympics will be held from July 26 to Aug 11.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 98, \"end\": 101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.320367394442262e-15, \"text\": \"SPH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\"}, {\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"score\": 0.9604822703099307, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Advertise\", \"types\": [\"Q7377\", \"Q729\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\"}, {\"begin\": 243, \"end\": 257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: EPA-EFE  Kimberly Kwek  PublishedJul 25, 2024, 06:55 PM  UpdatedJul 25, 2024, 10:45 PM  PARIS-The City of Love is not in love with the Olympic Games - yet.\", \"from\": 296, \"to\": 458, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 312, \"end\": 320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kimberly_Brady\", \"score\": 0.9907001818510267, \"rank\": 0.008682035193428108, \"text\": \"Kimberly\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kimberly_Brady\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kimberly_Brady\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Paris welcomes the world on July 26 witha grand opening ceremony on the Seine, the city's residents are still warming up to this romance.\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 463, \"end\": 468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2695151138384007e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 535, \"end\": 540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.394864364328536e-14, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Parisians whom The Straits Times spoke to have expressed mixed feelings about the July 26 to Aug 11 Games.\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 708, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 617, \"end\": 634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Straits_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Straits Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Straits_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Straits_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some welcome the branding, tourism dollars and eyeballs that come with hosting the Olympics, while others point to the downsides of having a mega event in the heart of the city.\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 886, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Photographer Johanna Liscio noted that it is the perfect opportunity to showcase her home, though it has impacted her business.\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 901, \"end\": 908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anjouan\", \"score\": 0.9998162543073644, \"rank\": 0.00018377942341728264, \"text\": \"Johanna\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anjouan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anjouan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 28-year-old, who specialises in vacation, proposal and engagement photography under the Instagram handle@paris.spirit,typically gets about 10 bookings weekly, but business has dipped by about 60 per cent during this period, with iconic landmarks such as the Eiffel Tower cordoned off.\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1305, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The majority of her clients are tourists from Asia, Europe and North America.\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1384, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"Paris is one of the most visited cities in the world and it's great for us, for the economy, for tourism to host the Games.\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1519, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1396, \"end\": 1401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2695151138384007e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For my job, I am not as happy as I thought I'd be - it's a bit stressful that I have to adapt to the situation every day, it's a bit more complicated than expected.\\\"\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the lead-up to the Olympics, some Parisians have voiced their unhappiness over having to endure months of disruption as the cityprepared for the quadrennial event.\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1853, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Road closures and construction have inconvenienced locals, increasing travelling time within the city significantly.\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1971, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another concern is rising prices during the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 2026, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, the price of a single metro ticket has increased from \\u20ac2.15 (S$3) to \\u20ac4 from July 20 to Sept 8.\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2135, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Businesses in Olympic security zoneshave also struggled, with some restaurant owners experiencing 80 per cent fewer customers owing to stricter security measures.\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2299, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Private guide Vadim Sotropa said: \\\"It's important to understand that Parisians' discontent is not directed at the guests or athletes.\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2315, \"end\": 2320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Vadim\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.732554421138565e-20, \"text\": \"Vadim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Vadim\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Vadim\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is related to a series of government decisions that failed to balance their ambitious plans with the peaceful lives of the city's residents and country's needs.\\\"\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2599, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As a result, many are leaving the capital during the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2663, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Among them is a designer, who wanted to be identified only as Miranda.\", \"from\": 2665, \"to\": 2735, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 31-year-old will be escaping to the south of France for a few days, though she noted that the daily disruptions are minor compared to the plight of certain segments of Paris' population.\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2785, \"end\": 2791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999999439968335, \"rank\": 2.971633462949277e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2908, \"end\": 2913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2695151138384007e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"I feel like these are minor problems as compared to students getting unhoused, homeless people getting shipped off to god knows where and the cops coming to destroy their camping sites, and workers working illegally with no health insurance.\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 3180, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am more horrified by the choice of budget that's used for something that's not as important, as compared to using it for something that could help thousands of people.\\\"\", \"from\": 3182, \"to\": 3353, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A report released in June by the French collective Le Revers de la Medaille (The Other Side of the Medal), which represents 90 non-profit organisations that work with migrants and the homeless, detailed the expulsion of over 12,000 people from Paris since April 2023.\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3622, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3388, \"end\": 3394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8338435395360055, \"rank\": 0.18708100204884648, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3409, \"end\": 3415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Revers\", \"score\": 0.9999999997830855, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Revers\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Revers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Revers\"}, {\"begin\": 3599, \"end\": 3604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2695151138384007e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, there was the controversial decision to spend \\u20ac1.4 billion cleaning the Seine, which will host marathon swimming and the triathlon.\", \"from\": 3624, \"to\": 3761, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3702, \"end\": 3707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.394864364328536e-14, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Seine will host marathon swimming and the triathlon.\", \"from\": 3763, \"to\": 3819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3767, \"end\": 3772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.394864364328536e-14, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: EPA-EFE  The installation of an aluminium judging tower for the surfing event in Tahiti also drew ire for its environmental impact - there are concerns about damage to coral reef.\", \"from\": 3821, \"to\": 4007, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3909, \"end\": 3915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999968317752, \"rank\": 3.168096129404832e-09, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not all doom and gloom in Paris, though.\", \"from\": 4009, \"to\": 4055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4041, \"end\": 4046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2695151138384007e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sotropa and his wife will be attending the opening and closing ceremonies, and will catch events held at iconic venues such as the Eiffel Tower, the Hotel des Invalides, Grand Palais and Place de la Concorde.\", \"from\": 4056, \"to\": 4264, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4205, \"end\": 4224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hotel des Invalides\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\"}, {\"begin\": 4243, \"end\": 4263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4822000489619255e-23, \"text\": \"Place de la Concorde\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sotropa, 26, admitted that he was not always for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 4266, \"to\": 4328, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But now, he said: \\\"I am looking forward to the Olympics because I see it as a unique opportunity to be part of this event.\\\"\", \"from\": 4329, \"to\": 4452, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Describing it as a \\\"once-in-a-lifetime\\\" event, social media content creator Theo Guyon, 23, is happy to soak in the atmosphere, saying: \\\"I am not worried about the crowd, it will just be for a few weeks, and I think the Olympics are worth having for a little less comfort.\\\"\", \"from\": 4454, \"to\": 4727, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4530, \"end\": 4534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Theseus\", \"score\": 0.9999294321308444, \"rank\": 7.05728492011739e-05, \"text\": \"Theo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Theseus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Theseus\"}, {\"begin\": 4535, \"end\": 4540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Guyon\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 1.0466357066588853e-11, \"text\": \"Guyon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Guyon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_Guyon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Laurane Vepierre, who usually takes a one-hour commute from the Essonne region to Paris for her job, will be working remotely for most of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 4729, \"to\": 4880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4793, \"end\": 4800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Essonne\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.096268620219718e-29, \"text\": \"Essonne\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Essonne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Essonne\"}, {\"begin\": 4811, \"end\": 4816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2695151138384007e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she will watch the swimming or athletics events if the opportunity arises.\", \"from\": 4881, \"to\": 4959, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It happens at a different place every four years, so there are benefits for the different places in terms of reputation, image and economy,\\\" said Vepierre.\", \"from\": 4961, \"to\": 5117, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And it's the Olympics, it's a very cool atmosphere, sport always brings people together.\\\"\", \"from\": 5119, \"to\": 5209, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As for the legacy of the Paris Games, that remains to be seen, as Sotropa added: \\\"I believe that it will take a long time after the Paris Olympic Games have concluded to objectively assess their benefits or drawbacks, once the excitement has settled and the city has returned to its normal rhythm.\\\"\", \"from\": 5211, \"to\": 5509, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics 2024  Olympics  France  Tourism  E-paper  Newsletters  Podcasts  RSS Feed  About Us  Terms & Conditions  Personal Data Protection Notice  Need help?\", \"from\": 5511, \"to\": 5668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5536, \"end\": 5542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999999439968335, \"rank\": 2.971633462949277e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reach us here.\", \"from\": 5669, \"to\": 5683, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertise with us\", \"from\": 5685, \"to\": 5702, \"entities\": []}]}"